#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:4
msgid "View MaxFrame jobs with Logview"
msgstr "使用 Logview 查看 MaxFrame 作业"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:6
msgid ""
"Logview is a tool that records and displays the execution status of "
"MaxCompute jobs. It has been adapted for MaxFrame. This page describes "
"how to use Logview 2.0 to inspect MaxFrame job execution information."
msgstr ""
"Logview 是用于记录和展示 MaxCompute 作业执行状态的工具，并已适配 MaxFrame"
"。本页介绍如何使用 Logview 查看 MaxFrame 作业的执行信息。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:11
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概览"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:13
msgid ""
"Logview has been adapted for MaxFrame and supports the following "
"capabilities:"
msgstr "Logview 已适配 MaxFrame，支持以下能力："

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:16
msgid ""
"View execution records and elapsed time of all DAGs submitted from a "
"MaxFrame session."
msgstr "查看一个 MaxFrame session 中提交的所有 DAG 的执行记录和耗时。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:18
msgid ""
"Interactively view the execution order, runtime, operator topology, and "
"status relations of every Sub DAG inside a DAG."
msgstr ""
"交互式查看一个 DAG 内各个 Sub DAG 的执行顺序、运行时间、算子拓扑和状态"
"关系。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:20
msgid ""
"View the configuration, runtime status, memory and CPU resource usage of "
"each sub-instance."
msgstr "查看每个子实例的配置、运行状态，以及内存和 CPU 资源使用情况。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:23
msgid ""
"For general information about Logview, refer to `Use Logview to view job "
"information <https://help.aliyun.com/zh/maxcompute/user-guide/use-"
"logview-v2-0-to-view-job-information>`_. This page focuses on viewing "
"MaxFrame job information."
msgstr ""
"关于 Logview 的通用说明，请参考 `使用 Logview 查看作业信息 <https://help."
"aliyun.com/zh/maxcompute/user-guide/use-logview-v2-0-to-view-job-"
"information>`_。本页重点说明如何查看 MaxFrame 作业信息。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:28
msgid "MaxFrame Logview entrance"
msgstr "MaxFrame Logview 入口"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:30
msgid ""
"After you create a session with ``session = new_session(...)``, the "
"system automatically generates a URL that starts with "
"``https://logview.aliyun.com/logview``."
msgstr ""
"使用 ``session = new_session(...)`` 创建 session 后，系统会自动生成以 ``"
"https://logview.aliyun.com/logview`` 开头的 URL。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:34
msgid ""
"When you submit MaxFrame jobs from DataWorks, click the URL directly to "
"open the MaxFrame Logview UI."
msgstr ""
"如果从 DataWorks 提交 MaxFrame 作业，可以直接单击该 URL 打开 MaxFrame "
"Logview UI。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:36
msgid ""
"When you submit MaxFrame jobs from a local environment, call "
"``session.get_logview_address()`` to print the URL, then copy it into "
"your browser."
msgstr ""
"如果从本地环境提交 MaxFrame 作业，可以调用 ``session.get_logview_address("
")`` 打印 URL，然后复制到浏览器中打开。"

