msgstr ""
"诊断辅助工具，包括 Progress Chart、Input Heat Chart、Output Heat Chart、"
"TaskTime Heat Chart 和 InstanceTime Heat Chart。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:1
msgid ""
"Refresh job execution status, switch to full screen or zoom the execution"
