#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:142
msgid "**Sub DAG node fields**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:144
msgid ""
"``STAGE_X``: Sub DAG name. The number indicates execution order, starting"
" from 1 and increasing."
msgstr "``STAGE_X``：Sub DAG 名称。数字表示执行顺序，从 1 开始递增。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:146
msgid ""
"``X/X/X`` (for example ``0/5/5``): Number of ODPS instances in different "
"states inside the current Sub DAG, in the order *running / completed / "
"total*."
msgstr ""
"``X/X/X``（例如 ``0/5/5``）：当前 Sub DAG 中不同状态的 ODPS instance 数量"
"，顺序为 *running / completed / total*。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:149
msgid "Start and end time."
msgstr "开始和结束时间。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:150
msgid "``MCSQL``: Engine that executes the current Sub DAG."
msgstr "``MCSQL``：执行当前 Sub DAG 的引擎。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:151
msgid ""
"``OP 1``: Number of operators contained in the current Sub DAG. Double-"
"click the node to view the operator graph."
msgstr ""
"``OP 1``：当前 Sub DAG 包含的 operator 数量。双击节点可查看 operator "
"graph。"

