msgid "Sub DAG list"
msgstr "Sub DAG 列表"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:157
msgid ""
"This list shows the runtime information of all Sub DAGs in the current "
"DAG, sorted by time."
msgstr "该列表按时间顺序展示当前 DAG 中所有 Sub DAG 的运行信息。"

