msgid "Progress"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:1
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Sub DAG progress. Reaching 100% in the Running state only means all "
"instances scheduled so far have finished, not that the Sub DAG itself is "
"complete."
msgstr ""
"Sub DAG 进度。在 Running 状态下达到 100% 只表示当前已调度的所有 instance "
"已完成，并不表示 Sub DAG 本身已经完成。"

