msgid "This list shows the ODPS instance jobs related to the Sub DAG."
msgstr "该列表展示与 Sub DAG 相关的 ODPS instance jobs。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:1
msgid "Instance ID"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:1
msgid "ID of the ODPS instance job."
msgstr "ODPS instance job 的 ID。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:1
msgid "Instance status. See *Instance status values* below."
msgstr "Instance 状态。参见下方 *Instance status values*。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:1
msgid "Job details."
msgstr "作业详情。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:1
msgid "Job submission time."
msgstr "作业提交时间。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:1
msgid "Job completion time."
msgstr "作业完成时间。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:1
msgid "Job runtime."
msgstr "作业运行耗时。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:188
msgid "**Instance status values**"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:190
msgid "**Failed**: Execution failed."
msgstr "**Failed**：执行失败。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:191
msgid "**Cancelled**: The job was cancelled."
msgstr "**Cancelled**：作业已取消。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:192
msgid "**Running**: The job is running."
msgstr "**Running**：作业正在运行。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:193
msgid "**Terminated**: The job finished successfully."
msgstr "**Terminated**：作业已成功完成。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:194
msgid ""
"**Fallback**: The job was downgraded; a new instance record will be "
"created."
msgstr "**Fallback**：作业发生降级，会创建一条新的 instance 记录。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:196
msgid ""
"**Unknown_terminated**: The job has finished, but it is not known whether"
" it succeeded or failed."
msgstr "**Unknown_terminated**：作业已结束，但无法确定是成功还是失败。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:200
msgid "Fuxi Sensor"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:202
msgid ""
"Fuxi Sensor is the full-dimension resource view of a MaxFrame job. You "
"can use Fuxi Sensor to view the actual CPU and memory consumption of "
"every Fuxi instance. It is an essential tool for diagnosing job issues "
"and analyzing job runtime quality. For example, Fuxi Sensor helps with "
"the following scenarios:"
msgstr ""
"Fuxi Sensor 是 MaxFrame 作业的全维度资源视图。你可以通过 Fuxi Sensor 查看"
"每个 Fuxi instance 的实际 CPU 和内存消耗，它是诊断作业问题和分析作业运行"
"质量的重要工具。例如，Fuxi Sensor 可用于以下场景："

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:208
msgid "Determine the actual amount of memory used when a job runs out of memory."
msgstr "确认作业发生 OOM 时实际使用了多少内存。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:210
msgid "Inspect the resource usage of MaxFrame Fuxi instances:"
msgstr "查看 MaxFrame Fuxi instance 的资源使用情况："

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:212
msgid "**CPU usage**"
msgstr "**CPU 使用率**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:214
msgid ""
"The CPU chart contains two lines: one shows the requested CPU "
"(``cpu_plan``), the other shows the actual CPU usage (``cpu_usage``). On "
"the y-axis, ``400`` means 4 processors. The requested CPU can be adjusted"
" only by changing the number of processors. The actual CPU usage cannot "
"be tuned directly."
msgstr ""
"CPU 图表包含两条线：一条表示申请的 CPU（``cpu_plan``），另一条表示实际 "
"CPU 使用量（``cpu_usage``）。在 y 轴上，``400`` 表示 4 个 processor。申请"
"的 CPU 只能通过调整 processor 数量改变，实际 CPU 使用量无法直接调节。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:220
msgid "**Memory usage**"
msgstr "**内存使用量**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:222
msgid ""
"The memory chart contains two lines: requested memory (``mem_plan``) and "
"actual memory usage (``mem_usage``)."
msgstr ""
"内存图表包含两条线：申请内存（``mem_plan``）和实际内存使用量（``mem_usage"
"``）。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:226
msgid "Use cases"
msgstr "使用场景"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:229
msgid "View the longest-running stage"
msgstr "查看耗时最长的 stage"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:231
msgid ""
"The Timeline column in the DAG list, Sub DAG list, and Instance list lets"
" you quickly find the longest-running DAG, Sub DAG, or Instance at the "
"current level."
msgstr ""
"DAG 列表、Sub DAG 列表和 Instance 列表中的 Timeline 列，可帮助你快速找到"
"当前层级耗时最长的 DAG、Sub DAG 或 Instance。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:237
msgid ""
"When the list is long and paginated, sort the Duration column in "
"descending order to find the longest-running entries quickly."
msgstr ""
"当列表较长并分页展示时，可以按 Duration 列倒序排序，快速找到耗时最长的"
"条目。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:241
msgid "View the cause of an execution failure"
msgstr "查看执行失败原因"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:243
msgid ""
"When a DAG fails or the client returns an exception, follow these steps "
"in MaxFrame Logview:"
msgstr ""
"当 DAG 执行失败或客户端返回异常时，可以在 MaxFrame Logview 中按以下步骤"
"排查："

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:246
msgid "Check the status of every DAG in the DAG list."
msgstr "在 DAG 列表中查看每个 DAG 的状态。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:247
msgid ""
"Find the most recent DAG with status ``Failed`` and click the icon in the"
" **Detail** column to view the details."
msgstr "找到最近一个状态为 ``Failed`` 的 DAG，单击 **Detail** 列中的图标查看详情。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:249
msgid ""
"On the DAG details page, find the Sub DAG node displayed in red (for "
"example ``STAGE_1``). The **Result** page also shows the error message."
msgstr ""
"在 DAG 详情页中找到显示为红色的 Sub DAG 节点（例如 ``STAGE_1``）。**"
"Result** 页面也会展示错误信息。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:251
msgid ""
"Click the failed Sub DAG node ``STAGE_1``. In the Instance list, click "
"the icon in the **Detail** column to find the failed instance."
msgstr ""
"单击失败的 Sub DAG 节点 ``STAGE_1``。在 Instance 列表中，单击 **Detail** "
"列中的图标，定位失败的 instance。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:255
msgid "View operators contained in a Sub DAG"
msgstr "查看 Sub DAG 中包含的 operators"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:257
msgid "There are two ways to view the operators contained in a Sub DAG:"
msgstr "可以通过以下两种方式查看 Sub DAG 中包含的 operators："

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:259
msgid "**Method 1**: On the DAG details page, click the Sub DAG node."
msgstr "**方式 1**：在 DAG 详情页中，单击 Sub DAG 节点。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:260
msgid "**Method 2**: On the DAG details page, double-click the Sub DAG node."
msgstr "**方式 2**：在 DAG 详情页中，双击 Sub DAG 节点。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:264
msgid ""
"Each operator is annotated with the line of MaxFrame script code it "
"corresponds to."
msgstr "每个 operator 都会标注其对应的 MaxFrame 脚本代码行。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:266
msgid ""
"Some operators are tagged with ``merged from``. This means the optimizer "
"merged multiple operators after DAG submission to produce a new operator "
"with the same functionality but better performance."
msgstr ""
"部分 operators 会带有 ``merged from`` 标记，表示优化器在 DAG 提交后合并了"
"多个 operators，生成了功能相同但性能更好的新 operator。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:271
msgid "View table data"
msgstr "查看表数据"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:273
msgid "**View the data flow structure**"
msgstr "**查看数据流结构**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:275
msgid ""
"To inspect the data flow, double-click a Sub DAG node on the DAG details "
"page to enter the operator details page. Click the connection line "
"between two operators to view the data type, index, and column name "
"information."
msgstr ""
"如需查看数据流，在 DAG 详情页中双击某个 Sub DAG 节点进入 operator 详情页"
"。单击两个 operators 之间的连线，即可查看数据类型、index 和 column name "
"信息。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:280
msgid "The fields are described below:"
msgstr "字段说明如下："

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:282
msgid "``Type: dataframe``: The upstream operator outputs a ``dataframe``."
msgstr "``Type: dataframe``：上游 operator 输出 ``dataframe``。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:283
msgid "``DataFrame Index``: Index information."
msgstr "``DataFrame Index``：Index 信息。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:285
msgid ""
"``None: int64`` means the DataFrame contains a single unnamed index of "
"type ``int64``."
msgstr ""
"``None: int64`` 表示该 DataFrame 包含一个未命名、类型为 ``int64`` 的单级 "
"index。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:287
msgid "``DataFrame Columns``: Column information."
msgstr "``DataFrame Columns``：Column 信息。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:289
msgid ""
"``<column name>: <dtype>`` lists every column in the current DataFrame "
"with its data type."
msgstr "``<column name>: <dtype>`` 列出当前 DataFrame 中每个 column 及其数据类型。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:291
msgid "``DataFrame Level Names``: The level names of the current DataFrame."
msgstr "``DataFrame Level Names``：当前 DataFrame 的 level names。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:293
msgid "**View the data table structure**"
msgstr "**查看数据表结构**"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:295
msgid ""
"Click any operator graph or any ODPS Table node in the Sub DAG Graph to "
"view the table structure."
msgstr ""
"在 Sub DAG Graph 中单击任意 operator graph 或 ODPS Table 节点，即可查看表"
"结构。"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:299
msgid "View job details"
msgstr "查看作业详情"

#: ../../source/user_guide/general/logview.rst:301
msgid ""
"On the DAG details page, click the icon in the **Detail** column of the "
"Instance list to view the job details."
msgstr ""
"在 DAG 详情页中，单击 Instance 列表 **Detail** 列中的图标，即可查看作业"
"详情。"

